\" />"},{"pid":"c4e39f151a8fe62e89b5180cf02420fa03c66f3c","tid":1454471,"uid":130641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7e42f22f50bf123c36676c87c60bbdfcea3e03","tid":1454471,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"唔係想咁做，只係好奇問，如果而家所有手足撤退，d機係咪會resume?定係cancel咗就cancel咗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"我估應該唔會resume...出晒消息啲人都唔去機場..resume都盞被人屌..."},{"pid":"a634f20ceae89e09d8579284d920e2bd5851c0fd","tid":1454471,"uid":226594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"機管局稱機場運作受嚴重影響 除已登記航班其餘全部取消<br />\n<br />\n民間於今日8月12日再發起機場集會，行動於下午1時開始，現場大批民眾聚集。機管局指機場運作受嚴重影響，除已完成航班登機程序的離港航班，以及正前往香港的抵港航班外，其餘今日所有航班已全部取消。<br />\n<br />\n機管局表示機場運作受嚴重影響，除已完成航班登機程序的離港航班，以及正前往香港的抵港航班外，其餘今日所有航班已全部取消。旅客出發前往機場前查閱機場網頁或「我的航班」流動應用程式有關航班最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n部分前往機場巴士亦改道行駛，不停機場1號客運大樓站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/28385/%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%97%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-%E9%99%A4%E5%B7%B2%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%85%B6%E9%A4%98%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F28385%2F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF-%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25B6%25E9%25A4%2598%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%2F1%2F&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=558c4bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/28385/%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%97%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-%E9%99%A4%E5%B7%B2%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E8%88